    task6.state  
  • Classes in task6.state used by task6.state 
    Class and Description
    A_State
    Defines the shared elements a state in the state machine representing the vending machine.
    A_StateBuildCoffeeBase
    Defines the shared elements of the states that build the base ingredients.
    A_StateBuildCoffeeExtra
    Defines the shared elements of the states that build the extra ingredients.
    StateBuildCoffeeBaseDecaf
    Defines the state that builds the base decaf-coffee ingredient.
    StateBuildCoffeeBaseRegular
    Defines the state that builds the base regular-coffee ingredient.
    StateBuildCoffeeExtraCream
    Defines the state that builds the extra cream ingredient.
    StateBuildCoffeeExtraMilk
    Defines the state that builds the extra milk ingredient.
    StateBuildCoffeeExtraSugar
    Defines the state that builds the extra sugar ingredient.
    StateDeliverProduct
    Defines the state that delivers the final wrapped product.
    StateReturnChange
    Defines the state that returns change based on a completed transaction where a product was delivered.
    StateReturnRefund
    Defines the state that returns a refund based on an aborted transaction where a product was not delivered.
    StateStartTransaction
    Defines the state that starts a transaction by inserting money and selecting the base coffee ingredient.
